formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1.)The project Sahaj Century is being developed on the proportionate land ad-measuring 1409.60 Sq. Mtrs. out of total land area ad measuring 3851 Sq. Mtrs. The purchase cost, as per purchase deed dated on 10th August, 2011, of the proportionate land admeasuring 1409.60 Sq. Mtrs. is Rs. 1,92,16,827- is calculated and index cost of acquisition of the said land is Rs. 3,53,58,961/- (i.e. 1,92,16,827/- *184/ 100) and the Jantri value of the said land is Rs. 1,26,86,400/- (i.e. 1409.60 Sq. Mtrs. * 9000/- per sq. Mtrs.) As per RERA Circular No. 11/2018, Acquisition cost of land is to be Indexed cost of acquisition of land or Prevailing ASR Value, whichever is higher at the time of registration of Project. Accordingly, the Acquisition cost of land is taken as Rs.3,53,58,961/-.					

2.) The above certificate is issued on the  basis of the records and documents produced before me and explanations provided to me by the management of the firm; based on the verification of unaudited books of accounts till 31/07/2021.

3.)Inventory Details Of Project Has Been Provided And Confirmed By The Promoter. The Allottees Id And Mob No Are Written Dummy As And When They Are Unavailable  To me And Promoter Ensures To Provide Them In Next Return.  In This Quarter Return Following Allottee'S Id Is Provided Dummy.
